Creating an arrayName
=====================
dataType arrayName[]= new dataType[size];
eg:
 int marks[] = new int[50];
 int numbers[] = {1,2,3};
 int morenos[] = {4,5,6};
 String fruits[] = {"apple","banana","carrot"};

 To find length 
  arrayname.length

  +infinity 
  int largest =  Integer.MIN_VALUE;

  -infinity
  int lowest = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
  